{"id": "art-459", "label": "Art. 459", "title": "Art. 459: Admiterea în principiu", "slug": "art-459", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_619323991\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1481\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_619323991\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 459:\nAdmiterea în principiu </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_246617619\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1480\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_246617619\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)La primirea cererii de revizuire, se fixeaz&#259; termen\npentru examinarea admisibilit&#259;&#355;ii în principiu a cererii de\nrevizuire, pre&#351;edintele dispunând ata&#351;area dosarului cauzei.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_830547942\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1479\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_830547942\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)Admisibilitatea în principiu se examineaz&#259; de\nc&#259;tre instan&#355;&#259;, în camera de consiliu, cu citarea\np&#259;r&#355;ilor &#351;i cu participarea procurorului. Neprezentarea\npersoanelor legal citate nu împiedic&#259; examinarea admisibilit&#259;&#355;ii\nîn principiu.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_2094382885\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1478\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_2094382885\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)<b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'>Instan&#355;a\nexamineaz&#259; dac&#259;:</b></span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_2124358723\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1477\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_2124358723\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>a)<b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'>cererea a fost\nformulat&#259; în termen &#351;i de o persoan&#259; dintre cele prev&#259;zute\nla art. 455;</b></span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1789430356\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1476\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1789430356\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>b)cererea a fost întocmit&#259; cu respectarea prevederilor\nart. 456 alin. (2) &#351;i (3);</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_956700486\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1475\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_956700486\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>c)au fost invocate temeiuri legale pentru redeschiderea\nprocedurilor penale;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_599259949\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1474\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_599259949\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>d)faptele &#351;i mijloacele de prob&#259; în baza\nc&#259;rora este formulat&#259; cererea nu au fost prezentate într-o cerere\nanterioar&#259; de revizuire care a fost judecat&#259; definitiv;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1261102371\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1473\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1261102371\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>e)faptele &#351;i mijloacele de prob&#259; în baza\nc&#259;rora este formulat&#259; cererea conduc, în mod evident, la stabilirea\nexisten&#355;ei unor temeiuri legale ce permit revizuirea;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_735598854\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1472\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_735598854\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>f)persoana care a formulat cererea s-a conformat\ncerin&#355;elor instan&#355;ei dispuse potrivit art. 456 alin. (4).</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_770384599\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1471\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_770384599\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(4)În cazul în care instan&#355;a constat&#259; c&#259;\nsunt îndeplinite condi&#355;iile prev&#259;zute la alin. (3), dispune prin\nîncheiere admiterea în principiu a cererii de revizuire.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1846860879\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1470\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1846860879\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(5)În cazul în care instan&#355;a constat&#259;\nneîndeplinirea condi&#355;iilor prev&#259;zute la alin. (3), dispune prin\nsentin&#355;&#259; respingerea cererii de revizuire, ca inadmisibil&#259;.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_44578959\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1469\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_44578959\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(6)Când cererea de revizuire a fost f&#259;cut&#259; pentru\nun condamnat decedat sau când condamnatul care a f&#259;cut cererea ori în\nfavoarea c&#259;ruia s-a f&#259;cut revizuirea a decedat dup&#259; introducerea\ncererii, prin excep&#355;ie de la dispozi&#355;iile art. 16 alin. (1) lit. f),\nprocedura de revizuire î&#351;i va urma cursul, iar în cazul rejudec&#259;rii\ncauzei, dup&#259; admiterea în principiu, instan&#355;a va hot&#259;rî potrivit\ndispozi&#355;iilor art. 16, care se aplic&#259; în mod corespunz&#259;tor.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_188701944\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1468\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_188701944\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(7)Încheierea prin care este admis&#259; în principiu\ncererea de revizuire este definitiv&#259;. Sentin&#355;a prin care este\nrespins&#259; cererea de revizuire, dup&#259; analiza admisibilit&#259;&#355;ii\nîn principiu, este supus&#259; aceleia&#351;i c&#259;i de atac ca &#351;i\nhot&#259;rârea la care se refer&#259; revizuirea.</span></p>"}